**Remote OK**
RemoteOK is a job board focused on remote work opportunities across tech, design, marketing, and other professional fields.
It aggregates listings from companies looking to hire distributed talent, letting you filter roles by type, tech stack, and experience level.
The platform is widely used by people who want flexible, location‑independent jobs without sorting through traditional office‑based listings.

Link: https://remoteok.com/


